UniCast Network


















DDoS Protected Network














Geographically Redundant DNS
We have servers in North America, South America, Europe, Asia and Australia.



DDoS Protection
We offer DDoS Protected DNS servers, if your business is under a risk and need 365x7x24 Uptime.



Supported DNS records
A, MX, CNAME, TXT, SPF, NS, AAAA, SRV, RP, and SOA records



Web redirects
We support both 301 and 302 HTTP redirect. Iframes are available too.



DNS statistics
You can see how many requests have the DNS servers for your domain per year, month, day or hour.



Mail forwards
Don't have a mail server? Forward all e-mails sent to your domain to your personal e-mail in GMail, Yahoo or others.



Native IPv6 Support
Most of our DNS servers are with Native IPv6 Support. Be ready for the future of the Internet.



Secondary DNS
Manage all DNS settings on your master server. We will auto-update all settings on our servers.



Dynamic DNS
You have Dynamic IP addresses on your devices and need access to them? Use our Dynamic DNS and auto-update your A and AAAA records.


















